ARM: dts: r8a7742-iwg21d-q7: Sound DMA support via DVC on DTS

Enable sound with DMA support on carrier board.

DMA transfer uses DVC

     DMA               DMApp
[MEM] -> [SRC] -> [DVC] -> [SSIU] -> [SSI]

     DMA               DMApp
[MEM] <- [DVC] <- [SRC] <- [SSIU] <- [SSI]

